WEBVTT

00:00:01.272 --> 00:00:02.649
Pata picha hii:

00:00:02.649 --> 00:00:03.742
Ni Jumatatu asubuhi,

00:00:03.742 --> 00:00:04.861
upo ofisini,

00:00:04.861 --> 00:00:06.615
unakaa sawa kwa ajili ya kuanza siku ya kazi,

00:00:06.615 --> 00:00:09.437
na mtu uliyekutana nae wakati upo jengo la chini,

00:00:09.437 --> 00:00:11.273
anaingia kwenye kijiofisi chako

00:00:11.273 --> 00:00:12.675
na kuiba kiti chako.

00:00:12.675 --> 00:00:13.917
Hasemi neno lolote ---

00:00:13.917 --> 00:00:15.305
anaondoka nacho tu.

00:00:15.305 --> 00:00:17.788
Hakupi sababu yoyote ni kwa nini amechukua kiti chako

00:00:17.788 --> 00:00:19.899
na kuacha viti vyote vilivyopo katika jengo hilo

00:00:19.899 --> 00:00:22.041
Hatambui kwamba utahitaji kiti chako

00:00:22.041 --> 00:00:23.582
ili kukamilisha kazi siku ya leo.

00:00:23.582 --> 00:00:24.979
Hutapigania

00:00:24.979 --> 00:00:27.866
Utamfata yule mtu katika kijiofisi chake

00:00:27.866 --> 00:00:30.215
na kusema "Kwanini uchukue kiti changu?"